@startuml 25-proactive-suggestion
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Proactive AI Suggestion

participant "SuggestionDetector\n(BackgroundService)" as D
participant "AppDbContext" as CTX
database "suggestions" as DB
actor User
participant "HomePage" as UI
participant "GET /api/suggestions" as API
participant "POST /api/suggestions/{key}/dismiss" as DISMISS
participant "SearchResults / Ask" as TGT

== Detect ==
D -> CTX: load last 14d interactions per user
D -> D: apply heuristics
D -> CTX: UPSERT Suggestion (by Key)
CTX -> DB: INSERT/UPDATE

== Render ==
User -> UI: load home
UI -> API: GET /api/suggestions
API -> CTX: active (DismissedAt null, age<7d)
CTX -> DB: SELECT
DB --> API: row | none
alt row
    API --> UI: suggestion
    UI --> User: gradient card + [Primary] [Dismiss]
else none
    API --> UI: 204
    UI -> UI: hide card, shift stacks up
end

== Primary ==
User -> UI: tap primary action
UI -> TGT: navigate /search?... or /ask?q=...

== Dismiss ==
User -> UI: tap Dismiss
UI -> DISMISS: POST /api/suggestions/{key}/dismiss
DISMISS -> CTX: UPDATE DismissedAt = now
CTX -> DB: UPDATE
DB --> CTX: ok
DISMISS --> UI: 204
UI -> UI: hide card
note right of UI
  Key suppressed for 7 days
end note

@enduml
